# ESP8266 example using Arduino IDE

## Install PubSubClient library
In Arduino IDE, press ctrl + shift + i, it will open the Library Manager. Search for PubSubClient by Nick O'Leary and install the latest version.

## Install ArduinoJson library
In Arduino IDE, press ctrl + shift + i, it will open the Library Manager. Search for ArduinoJson by Benoit Blanchon and install the latest version.

## If you happen to not have the ESP8266 board files yet
Follow this tutorial: https://randomnerdtutorials.com/how-to-install-esp8266-board-arduino-ide/
